<Base title="Services — Shepparton Home Organising">
  <section class="container">
    <h1>Services</h1>

    <div class="feature-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <div class="icon">⇄</div>
        <h2>NDIS Customized Support </h2>
        <p>Clear the excess and keep what serves you. We work zone by zone with a simple process: sort, decide, contain, label. I'll guide choices and organise donation or recycling where possible.</p>
        <p class="muted">Great for: pantries, wardrobes, kids' rooms, garages, linen cupboards.</p>
        <p><a class="link" href="contact/">Start decluttering</a></p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="icon">▦</div>
        <h2>Personal Space Design</h2>
        <p>Set up easy systems for everyday life. Think baskets, labels, and storage that actually fits your routines. I'll create a layout that's simple to maintain, whether you're a family of five or living solo.</p>
        <p><a class="link" href="contact/">Let's organise it</a></p>
      </article>

    </div>

    <div class="steps">
      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <ol class="step-list">
        <li><strong>Free phone chat (15 min):</strong> Your goals, your space, your timeline.</li>
        <li><strong>In-home or virtual assessment:</strong> Simple plan + estimate.</li>
        <li><strong>Session day:</strong> We work together with a calm, clear process.</li>
        <li><strong>Waste & donations:</strong> Where possible, managed for you.</li>
        <li><strong>Simple upkeep guide:</strong> A few habits so it stays tidy.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <p><a class="btn" href="contact/">Get your tailored quote</a></p>
  </section>
